        public MultiblockUIBuilder setWorkingStatus(boolean isWorkingEnabled,

      • setWorkingStatusKeys

        public MultiblockUIBuilder setWorkingStatusKeys(java.lang.String idlingKey,
                                                java.lang.String pausedKey,
                                                java.lang.String runningKey)
        Set custom translation keys for the three-state "Idling", "Paused", "Running" display text. You still must call addWorkingStatusLine() for these to appear!
        Pass any key as null for it to continue to use the default key.
        参数:
        idlingKey - The translation key for the Idle state, or "!isActive && isWorkingEnabled".
        pausedKey - The translation key for the Paused state, or "!isWorkingEnabled".
        runningKey - The translation key for the Running state, or "isActive".

      • addEnergyUsageLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addEnergyUsageLine(gregtech.api.capability.IEnergyContainer energyContainer)
        Adds the max EU/t that this multiblock can use.
        Added if the structure is formed and if the passed energy container has greater than zero capacity.

      • addEnergyTierLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addEnergyTierLine(int tier)
        Adds the max Recipe Tier that this multiblock can use for recipe lookup.
        Added if the structure is formed and if the passed tier is a valid energy tier index for GTValues.VNF.

      • addEnergyUsageExactLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addEnergyUsageExactLine(long energyUsage)
        Adds the exact EU/t that this multiblock needs to run.
        Added if the structure is formed and if the passed value is greater than zero.

      • addEnergyProductionLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addEnergyProductionLine(long maxVoltage,
                                                   long recipeEUt)
        Adds the max EU/t that this multiblock can produce.
        Added if the structure is formed and if the max voltage is not zero and greater than the recipe EU/t.

      • addEnergyProductionAmpsLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addEnergyProductionAmpsLine(long maxVoltage,
                                                       int amperage)
        Adds the max EU/t that this multiblock can produce, including how many amps. Recommended for multi-amp outputting multis.
        Added if the structure is formed, if the amperage is greater than zero and if the max voltage is greater than zero.

      • addComputationUsageLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addComputationUsageLine(int maxCWUt)

      • addComputationUsageExactLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addComputationUsageExactLine(int currentCWUt)

      • addWorkingStatusLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addWorkingStatusLine()

        Added if the structure is formed.

      • addWorkPausedLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addWorkPausedLine(boolean checkState)
        Adds the "Work Paused." line.
        Added if working is not enabled, or if the checkState passed parameter is false. Also added only if formed.

      • addRunningPerfectlyLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addRunningPerfectlyLine(boolean checkState)
        Adds the "Running Perfectly." line.
        Added if machine is active, or if the checkState passed parameter is false. Also added only if formed.

      • addIdlingLine

        public MultiblockUIBuilder addIdlingLine(boolean checkState)
        Adds the "Idling." line.
        Added if the machine is not active and working is enabled, or if the checkState passed parameter is false. Also added only if formed.

        参数:

        maxProgress - total progress to be made.
